# [ANRW](../wg/anrw.html)

## Summary

The Applied Networking Research Workshop (ANRW) session at IETF 126 focused on **Transport and Media**. The session featured presentations on transport-layer enhancements, media streaming optimizations, multipath scheduling, Quality of Experience (QoE)-aware resource sharing, and implementations of IETF Transport Services (TAPS) and Media over QUIC (MoQ). 

